<br>
-Reboot the computer<br>
-Press the F8 key in 1 second intervals right after it does the memory test<br>
-You should get a menu screen; select the &quot;safe mode&quot; option<br>
-When Windows loads into safe mode, go to control panel, and select &quot;system&quot; (near the bottom of the screen)<br>
-Click the second tab on the top (Device Manager)<br>
-Double-click on &quot;Display Adapters&quot;<br>
-There should only be one graphics card selected; if not- remove the one that is NOT your video card<br>
<br>
